# Port Controller

## Usage

### 1. enable thrift

`./nb_port_controller -rpc`

### 2. select unit test freqeuncy

`./nb_port_controller loop <freq>`   , freq > 0  

## Compiling rpc client alone

```bash
make docker  # Create once
make attach
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/local/lib
cd /nb_ports_controller
make all  # TODO: Currently fpga is bundled with nb_ports_controller
cd thrift
make idl; make c_client;
```
